      name: "Milrinone (Primacor)",
      type: "Phosphodiesterase-3 (PDE3) inhibitor — inodilator",
      action: "Inhibits PDE3 in cardiac and vascular smooth muscle, increasing intracellular cAMP → enhanced cardiac contractility (positive inotropy) AND vasodilation (reduces preload and afterload); shifts ESPVR slope upward while reducing end-diastolic pressure",
